                <p class="ia-table-text">No gross cost to business. </p>
                <p class="ia-table-text" />
                <p class="ia-table-text">Familiarisation costs to business are explained and accounted for in the separate and complementary assessment of the proposed changes to land-use planning regulations in order to transpose Seveso III.  They are not repeated here in order to avoid double-counting.  No other costs have been identified.  </p>
